Label: has right
Definition: Indicates use or applicability of Right

Label: is exercised at
Definition: Indicates context or information about exercising a right

Label: dpv:hasStatus
Definition: Indicates the status of a Right Exercise Activity

Label: dpv:hasRecipient
Definition: Indicates the Recipient of a Right Exercise Activity

Label: dpv:isImplementedByEntity
Definition: Indicates the Entity that implements or performs a Right Exercise Activity

Label: foaf:page
Definition: Indicates a web page or document providing information or functionality associated with a Right Exercise

Label: dct:hasPart
Definition: Specifying a RightExerciseRecord has RightExerciseActivity as part of its records

Label: dct:isPartOf
Definition: Specifying a RightExerciseActivity is part of a RightExerciseRecord

Label: dpv:isBefore
Definition: Specifying a RightExerciseActivity occurs before another RightExerciseActivity

Label: dpv:isAfter
Definition: Specifying a RightExerciseActivity occurs before another RightExerciseActivity

Label: dpv:hasJustification
Definition: Specifying a justification for non-fulfilment of Right Exercise

Label: dct:format
Definition: Specifying the format of provided information, for example a CSV dataset

Label: dct:accessRights
Definition: Specfiying constraints on access associated with Rights Exercising (e.g. User must log in) or access to provided data (e.g. access via link)

Label: dct:valid
Definition: Specfiying the temporal validity of an activity associated with Right Exercise. For example, limits on duration for providing or accessing provided information
